## Task 5: Business Rule Validation

### Missing Region
- Missing values in the region field were replaced with "Unknown".
- All affected records were counted and reported in the data quality report.

### Missing Ship Mode
- Missing values in the ship_mode field were replaced with "Unknown".
- All affected records were counted and reported in the data quality report.

### Missing Discount
- Missing discount values were replaced with 0 only when all related sales fields were valid.
- Records that did not meet this condition were flagged for review.

### Negative Discount
- Records containing negative discount values were flagged as invalid.
- No automatic correction was applied.

### Discount Above Allowed Range
- Discount values exceeding the allowed business range were flagged as invalid.
- These records were included in the data quality report.

### Cancelled Orders
- Cancelled orders were retained in the dataset for record purposes.
- They were excluded from completed sales calculations and summary reports.

### Failed Payments
- Orders with failed payment status were retained in the dataset.
- They were excluded from completed sales calculations and summary reports.

### Refunded Orders
- Refunded orders were retained in the dataset.
- A separate refund summary was created for reporting purposes.

### Invalid Shipping Records
- Records where ship_date was earlier than order_date were flagged as invalid shipping records.
- These records were included in the data quality report.
